        <div class="post-text">I think 'The Golden Patch' was believed to exist by beta testers more than anyone.  We watched the game crawl along throughout the beta testing process with so few changes, we all believed there was going to be some giant patch the last week of testing.  I mean, it just wasn't possible they were going to release it the way it was, right?  When it didn't come, we believed it would be before release.  Shocked when the game was released and most of the issues remained, we were sure it would happen the first month.  And then... well, the downward cycle of despair as we watched, and never saw things drastically improve. <br /> <br />I think these next couple months will be make or break time, but especially patch 1.18.  Yoshi-P has set some high expectations with all this info.  I hope he can deliver. <br /> <br />As I've done since closed beta, I remain vigilant.  And I camp the mythical Golden Patch, waiting for it to pop.  And when it does, please let it drop phat lootz.</div>
